Class FlexibleGrid<E extends Spatializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.pavie.opennetworkmap.model.draw.network.grid.FlexibleGrid<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The class of objects you want to store

    public class FlexibleGrid<E extends Spatializable>
extends java.lang.Object
    A flexible grid is a two-dimensions list where you can store objects. Objects are added in function of other elements' place in grid.
